name: DYL Ventures
overview:
A Pakistan based venture capital firm and consultancy that helps entrepreneurs build their internet startups and marketing plans.

Founded by experts in the field of eCommerce and digital business models, DYL Ventures wants to help the first group of Pakistani entrepreneurs to build sustainable business models. With its primary focus on the entrepreneurs rather than the business model, DYL Ventures is betting in the open market space of Pakistan, and its talented individuals ability to change the internet landscape locally.
